item.title: About
item.description: Hi there! I’m Alan, a software engineering student with a knack for building things and a burning passion for innovative tech. This website is a product of my current dive into the world of Go. As I explore this language, I wanted to create a space to track my own progress, share my learnings, and hopefully, benefit other Go enthusiasts just like me on their own journeys.
